{"id":318,"date":"2024-08-02T14:57:49","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T14:57:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=318"},"modified":"2024-11-22T17:26:52","modified_gmt":"2024-11-22T17:26:52","slug":"hm03-surf","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/","title":{"rendered":"HM03 Surf"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">HM03 Surf<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Given to you from your rival on Route 12 after acquiring the ability to Mega Evolve your Pok\u00e9mon.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Badge Required<\/th>\n<td>Battery Badge (Dehara City Gym)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>A big wave crashes down on the foe. Can also be used for crossing waters.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Tarmigan Town<\/li>\n<li>Defeat Successor Maxima at Tarmigan Town<\/li>\n<li>Obtain the Battery Badge (to use Surf outside of battle)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>From outside of the Tarmigan Town Pok\u00e9mon Center take the path to right that\u2019s going North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-tarmigan-town-poke-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Tarmigan Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Tarmigan Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly reach a connector you want to enter.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-connector-leading-to-route-12.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the connector leading to Route 12. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the connector leading to Route 12.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue heading North to exit the connector and get to Route 12.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-exiting-the-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Exiting the connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exiting the connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The first time you take this path on Route 12 after defeating Successor Maxima at Tarmigan Town, you\u2019ll be stopped by your rival and challenged to a battle. You\u2019ll get the HM for Surf after defeating your rival.<\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table left grey\" style=\"min-width:900px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"6\" class=\"tableheader\">Rival<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-rival.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-toucannon.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-mamoswine.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-vaporeon.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-pupitar.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-fraxure.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Pok\u00e9mon<\/th>\n<td>Toucannon (Level 45)<\/td>\n<td>Mamoswine (Level 46)<\/td>\n<td>Vaporeon (Level 46)<\/td>\n<td>Pupitar (Level 47)<\/td>\n<td>Fraxure (Level 46)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Normal\/Flying<\/td>\n<td>Ice\/Ground<\/td>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<td>Rock\/Ground<\/td>\n<